timelineItems.desc: The New York Red Bulls look to get revenge on the team that ended their 2013 MLS Cup hopes, the Houston Dynamo, in midweek action at Red Bull Arena.
timelineItems.title: KICKOFF: New York Red Bulls vs. Houston Dynamo
